snippet.title: You Will Fall - OUT NOW
snippet.description:
Play You Will Fall!
Newgrounds: https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/880162
Itch: https://yaen-games.itch.io/you-will-fall

Join our discord server: https://discord.com/invite/eAQbA2bATF

You Will Fall is a psychological tightrope balancing game. While you try to get to the other side of a deep abyss between buildings, a voice inside your head taunts and tricks you to make you fall down and give up. Over and over again. Will you be able to make it across at some point? Find out now!
